    <string name="manual_title">User Manual</string>
    <string name="manual_how_to">How to use Security Guard</string>
    <string name="manual_steps">1. Set your secret Security Code in Settings.\n\n2. Add Master Numbers who are authorized to control your phone.\n\n3. SMS Commands (Replace \'CODE\' with your secret code):\n\n4• \'CODE Ring\' - Phone will ring even on silent.\n\n   • \'CODE Camera Front\' - Capture front camera photo.\n\n   • \'CODE Camera Back\' - Capture back camera photo.\n\n   • \'CODE Location On\' - Turn on GPS via accessibility.\n\n   • \'CODE Data on\' - Turn on Mobile Data via accessibility.\n\n   •\n4. Make sure to Enable Accessibility Service for Location/Data/Flight commands to work.</string>
    <string name="manual_tip">Tip: Commands are case-insensitive. \'CODE ring\' and \'CODE Ring\' both work.\n\nTip: Make sure Accessibility permission is on .</string>
